# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SECTION F — TURBOREPO + BUILD PIPELINE
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Reference: [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json)

## F1. Pipeline Tasks

| Task         | What it does                                  |
|--------------|-----------------------------------------------|
| `build`      | Compiles all apps (depends on `^build`)       |
| `dev`        | Starts all dev servers (persistent, no cache) |
| `lint`       | ESLint on all packages (depends on `^lint`)   |
| `type-check` | `tsc --noEmit` on all packages                |
| `test`       | Jest on all packages (no cache)               |

- `lint` and `type-check` are **separate tasks from `build`** by design.
  The web-app Vercel build skips them (`ignoreDuringBuilds: true`) to prevent hangs.
  They run via CI (`ci.yml`) instead.

## F2. Running Tasks

```bash
# Root-level (runs across all apps via Turborepo)
pnpm dev              → Start all dev servers
pnpm build            → Build all apps
pnpm lint             → Lint all apps
pnpm type-check       → Type-check all apps

# App-specific
pnpm --filter web-app dev
pnpm --filter desktop-agent build
pnpm --filter kavach-student-mobile test
```

## F3. Vercel Deployment

- Deployed via root [vercel.json](mdc:vercel.json):
  - Build command: `turbo run build --filter=web-app`
  - Output directory: `.next` (relative to `apps/web-app`)
  - Install command: `pnpm install`
- Vercel root directory MUST be set to the **repo root** (not `apps/web-app`).
- PWA files (`sw.js`, `workbox-*.js`) are generated at build time — gitignored.
- `prepare` script is `husky || true` to prevent Husky crashing on Vercel.

